                "Text": "Without revealing my age (suffice to say - over 60) I have to say I've come late to the subject of physics and all its branches. And what a subject it is!  This book by Jim Al Khalili is most enthralling - I was unable to put it down in spite of the fact that my brain seemed to be splitting in all directions!  Mr Al Khalili writes about the most amazing concepts in a clear and interesting fashion and never once 'talks down' to his readers."
